title: NATO Deputy Secretary to visit Portugal (NATO - North Atlantic Treaty Organisation)
text: ( Source : NATO - North Atlantic Treaty Organisation ) On Tuesday 20 October 2015 , the NATO Deputy Secretary General , Ambassador Alexander Vershbow will host the NATO-Industry Forum in Lisbon . This forum is co-organised by Supreme Allied
